show.title: Hero of the Construction Site
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/xr9q3w
show.description: Heroes of the Construction Site is a Story of two Families involved with a number of Labors and Construction Company Owners / share holders, A soft Story of a family wife demise and a sweet entry of a lady as a mother of the girl child who lost her mother and have seen struggles since childhood days due to her parents struggle centered with the construction site hazards, finally The Lady owner of the Construction company ties knot with the leader of labors , the father of the child, his courageous movements for company as a leader and his honesty towards his wife and child made the lady fall in love with him , they lived happy after.
